SALES MANAGEMENT

USERS
	- Manager
	- Seller

USER FUNCTIONALITY
	1.MANAGER
		- add,edit,delete product inventory
		- suggest product selling price
		- manage product loss
		- add,edit,delete expenses category
        - Manager can choose discount method per prodcut (by rate/ amount)
		- view income statement
		- view report per specific time period
		- manager system users (add,edit/delete)
        - Manager can choose seeling algorithm (FIFO/LIFO)
        - add,edit.delete role
        - assign permissions to role

	2.SELLER
		- sell product
		- add,edit,update,delete customer

SYSTEM FUNCTIONALITY
	- generate transaction/receipt number for each sale
	- update sales product table after each sale
	- can generate barcode for particular product

MODELS
	1.USER
		-id
		-fname
		-lname
		-email
		-password
		-role_id
		-active(bool)
		-softDelete

	2.ROLE
		-id
		-name

	3.CUSTOMER
		-id
		-name

	4.PRODUCT
		-id
		-name
		-hasSize(boolean)
        -softDelete

    5.INVENTORY (has many products)
        -id
        -issuer
        -totalCost
        -expectedAmount
        -description
        -issuer
        -finished(boolean)

	6.INVENTORYPRODUCT
		-id
		-product_id
        -inventory_id
		-quantity
		-cost
		-sellingPrice
        -discounts(json) eg. [10:1000,20:10%,30:2000]
        -discount_type_id

	7.LOSS
		-id
        -inventory_product_id
		-quantity
		-amount //can manually be typed
        -description

	8.EXPENSETYPE
		-id
		-name
		-description
        -role // required role to issue this type of expense

	9.EXPENSE
		-id
		-type
		-amount
		-description //optional
		-issuer

	10.PAYMENTTYPE
		-id
		-name
		-description

	11.SALE
		-id
        -inventory_product_id
		-quantity
		-sellingPrice	//before discount
		-buyingPrice
		-discount	//discount amount(per item)/can be manually typed
		-receipt_id

	12.RECEIPT
		-id
		-number
		-paymentType
		-customer_id	//nullable
        -issuer //user

    13.DISCOUNTTYPE
        -id
        -type (rate/amount)

    14.PERMISSION  //initialized
        -id
        -name

    15.ROLEPERMISSION
        -id
        -role_id
        -permission_id
